id: hac-s43s
title: Publish tagged releases with npm provenance and Bun consumption proof
description: "Convert publishing to a tag-driven, idempotent workflow that publishes once to npm with provenance, then verifies registry availability and launch behavior through both npx and bunx before creating the GitHub release."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 0
